author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at why sites like YouTube are taking AI so seriously. The biggest AI companies need to make numbers look healthy and the way to do that is stuff this technology even when it isn't needed into everything. AI isn't evil and their are ways to ethically use it, I'll show you how. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: I Don't Want YouTube To Keep Pushing AI...
